desc_short	-----								Krai Mira is a post-apocalyptic RPG that takes place on radioactive wastelands and swamps, dead settlements, caves and forests of the same-named island. Get the weapon you are most fit for, find comrades-in-arms, explore the island to find out the truth, and punish those who ravaged your world.							
developer									TallTech studio								
